## Installation

```bash
# Install dependencies
bun install

# Build the plugin
nx build <%= projectName %>

# Pack the plugin for distribution
nx pack <%= projectName %>
```

## Development

The main plugin logic is in `src/index.ts`. Implement your OpenCode plugin functionality there.

## Usage

```typescript
import { pluginName } from '@<%= npmScope %>/<%= projectName %>';

console.log(pluginName()); // <%= projectName %>
```

## Building

```bash
nx build <%= projectName %>
```

